    <div class="active" id="showproduct">
      <h1 class='title' align="center">敝帚自珍·丰子恺艺术展</h1>
      

<script src="/Templates/cn2014/js/ShopShow.js"></script>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>
      <div class="editor" id="metbox">
        <div class="box" >
          <div><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><img src="/upLoad/product/month_1612/201612292213564462.jpg"/></span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">《丰子恺艺术展》是浙江省博物馆馆藏丰子恺先生晚年创作的经典之作。先生在“文化大革命”期间遭受冲击，但他仍在艰难的环境中追忆旧作，笔耕不辍。丰子恺先生认为这些作品“虽甚草率，而笔力反胜于昔”。作为先生晚年最后的画集，可视为对自己一生画作的提炼，正如其在该画集自序中所言“今生画缘尽于此矣”。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">此次展览是我馆与浙江省博物馆再次成功合作举办的“大师作品走进潍坊”系列展内容之一。展览分为“童心”、“世相”、“朋情”、“物我”四部分内容，集百余幅大师晚年精品，以展示先生的艺术风格。作品简洁趣味,单线勾描,情景一目了然，却让人意味无穷。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 43px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11px; FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; BACKGROUND: rgb(0,0,0); COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; text-underline: rgb(0,0,0)">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><img title="2.jpg" alt="2.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830208814723234.jpg"/><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><img title="3.jpg" alt="3.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830208905491453.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">“童心”：西风梨枣山园，儿童偷把长杆。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 104px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">莫遣旁人惊去，老夫静处闲看。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="4.jpg" alt="4.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830209539074370.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">“世相”：天涯静处无征战，兵气销为日月光。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="6.jpg" alt="6.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830209853046857.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">“朋情”：把酒话桑麻。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><img title="5.jpg" alt="5.jpg" src="/upload/image/20161229/14830210031307309.jpg"/><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">“物我”：人散后，一钩新月如水。</span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">丰子恺（1898年11月9日－1975年9月15日）</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">浙江省嘉兴市桐乡市石门镇人。原名丰润，又名仁、仍，号子</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">顗</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">，后改为子恺，笔名</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">TK。以中西融合画法创作漫画，以及散文而著名。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">丰子恺先生是新文化运动的启蒙者之一，是浙江近代颇具影响力的文艺大家。他集画家、文学家、翻译家和艺术教育家于一身，以一支笔、一颗心创造了一个诗意、真挚的艺术世界。先生早年师从李叔同学习绘画、音乐，并受其佛学思想的影响。“五四运动</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">以后，开始进行漫画创作。其艺术成就以</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">子恺漫画</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">影响最为深远。</span></span></p><p style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 32px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">&nbsp;丰子恺</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%">先生</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">自幼习诗文书画，有传统文化的“童子功</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">，后来又学西洋画，掌握了扎实的素描技巧和西洋画理论，具备了</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">融合东西</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">的条件。他在东瀛游学又及时地遇上竹久梦二这股强劲的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">东风</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">，将其灵性之火点燃，原先各行其道的西洋画技巧与传统的艺术修养，于此时融为一体，开始踏上一条左右逢源的艺术之道。</span></span></p><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16px; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">丰子恺先生的早期漫画作品多取自现实题材，带有“温情的讽刺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">，后期常作古诗新画，特别喜爱儿童题材。子恺漫画，风格简易朴实、意境隽永含蓄、充满现实主义的人文关怀。在他描绘的人间百态中，他用敏感细腻的视角，向我们展现那些容易被忽略的情趣瞬间，有温馨、有讽刺、有同情、有愤怒、也有悲悯，微小而不失深刻。朱自清曾将丰子恺的漫画比作</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">带核儿的小诗</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">，以为其有着橄榄般的悠长回味，而俞平伯则以为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">子恺漫画</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">如</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">“</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">一片片落英都含蓄着人间的情味</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">”</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri">。他的作品处处体现着对家人的亲情、朋友的友情、生活的热情，以及对万物的深情。</span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=176"></script>
            <div id="metinfo_additional"></div>
          </div>
